  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_405">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_405</del:identifier>
    <del:text>The special European Council last week gave a strong impetus to our work on European defence. The EU leaders had the first concrete discussion based on options tabled by the Commission. The President of the Commission presented them this morning. The EU leaders will continue their discussion on the European Council meetings next week and in June. As presidency of the Council, we stand ready to proactively take forward all initiatives that will reinforce European defence. I look forward to our continued exchange on this key topic and, of course, the forthcoming white paper on the future of European defence.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T19:54:47</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_2"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_211">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_211</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Petra Steger</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PfE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_71">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_71</del:identifier>
    <del:text>But, as you are from the Socialist Party from Spain, just a very small, tiny question: what is your opinion on why Spain has provided so little help to Ukraine currently? Because when you look at the GDP, the real help 芒聙聯 military aid 芒聙聯 it has given to Ukraine, it's almost nothing compared to Poland, Estonia, Denmark, Finland and so on. So, why is there so much talk and no actions? What is the problem in Spain with the Socialists? Why are you not acting?</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T11:18:50</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_62"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_233">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_233</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Diese Regelungen aus dem letzten Jahrhundert geh脙露ren abgeschafft,脗聽denn gerade bei lebenswichtigen Arzneimitteln ist die 脙露ffentliche Gesundheit keine nationale, sondern eine europ脙陇ische Frage. Den Critical Medicines Act begr脙录脙聼e ich ausdr脙录cklich, aber seien wir ehrlich: Wenn wir wirklich eine europaweite Versorgung sicherstellen wollen, dann m脙录ssen wir tiefer ansetzen und endlich die legislativen Wurzeln von Ausnahmen in den europ脙陇ischen Vertr脙陇gen selbst beseitigen.
Die Pandemie hat uns gezeigt: Krankheiten kennen keine Grenzen, und so sollten wir auch in Europa keine kennen. Denn Medikamente m脙录ssen dorthin, wo die Menschen sie brauchen脗聽芒聙聯 ganz ohne Grenzen.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:38:13</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_81"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_135">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_135</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Die ach so toleranten Mitstreiter im FEMM-Ausschuss beantragten ihre Ausladung, die dann auch prompt erfolgte. So ernst meinen es also unsere selbsternannten weiblichen Vork脙陇mpfer mit der politischen Teilnahme und der gleichen Repr脙陇sentation von Frauen. Nicht einmal in den eigenen weiblichen Reihen werden andere Meinungen toleriert. Reem Alsalem脗聽芒聙聯 merkt euch den Namen der echten K脙陇mpferin f脙录r Frauenrechte!</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:29:29</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_99"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_249">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_249</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Ruth Firmenich</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_NI"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_226">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_226</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Conhecemos, nos nossos pa脙颅ses, a experi脙陋ncia da rutura de medicamentos vitais (como anest脙漏sicos, antibi脙鲁ticos, mesmo insulina), como conhecemos o diagn脙鲁stico das nossas fragilidades: depend脙陋ncia de menos de um punhado de origens geogr脙隆ficas em mat脙漏rias芒聙聭primas e eros脙拢o da base industrial europeia.
A nossa a脙搂脙拢o 脙漏 urgente porque os resultados exigem tempo, e as respostas legislativas s脙拢o mesmo a parte mais f脙隆cil daquilo que precisamos de fazer. Sim, precisamos de uma lista de medicamentos cr脙颅ticos, de stocks de conting脙陋ncia, de novas pr脙隆ticas de aprovisionamento p脙潞blico. Precisamos mesmo de investir no fabrico europeu.
Mas n脙拢o basta. Precisamos de reconhecer que apenas com uma coordena脙搂脙拢o e investimento europeus comuns poderemos ser bem芒聙聭sucedidos nesta estrat脙漏gia, e que a disponibilidade de medicamentos no mercado n脙拢o serve os cidad脙拢os europeus, se o acesso, sob o ponto de vista da comportabilidade financeira, estiver em causa.
Sim, precisamos tamb脙漏m de falar do pre脙搂o dos medicamentos, e estes s脙拢o aspetos dos quais n脙拢o vamos desistir.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:29:13</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_73"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_513">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_513</del:identifier>
    <del:text>BDP u Siriji i dalje je manje od polovice vrijednosti iz 2011. godine. Infrastruktura naravno da je zna脛聧ajno o脜隆te脛聡ena, a ve脛聡ina Sirijaca 脜戮ivi i dalje u siroma脜隆tvu. Tro脜隆kovi ponovne izgradnje zemlje mogli bi se kretati pa do 200 milijardi eura.
Europska unija i njezine dr脜戮ave 脛聧lanice su mobilizirale ve脛聡 sada vi脜隆e od 35 milijardi, ali, naravno, pitanje je sada koji 脛聡e biti prioriteti na脜隆eg djelovanja. To naravno da jesu mir, sigurnost, jedinstvo zemlje, za脜隆tita svih manjina, ali posebno je zabrinjavaju脛聡a situacija kr脜隆脛聡ana. Do 2011. u Siriji je 脜戮ivjelo oko milijun kr脜隆脛聡ana, a danas ih je oko 300 tisu脛聡a i oni svaki dan strepe za vlastitu sigurnost.
Dakle, sve su manjine va脜戮ne, ali ako se Europa ne zauzme za kr脜隆脛聡ane, onda to nitko ne脛聡e. Stoga, ne smijemo ih zaboraviti.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:18:34</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_289"/>
  </rdf:Description>
