  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_459">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_459</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Eppure, nel vostro piano "Industria pulita" non riusciamo a ravvedere dei ravvedimenti sostanziali: confermate la folle corsa verso l'elettrico; sussurrate, appena, l'espressione "neutralit脙聽 tecnologica" e snobbate bellamente l'uso del nucleare per fini civili.
In pi脙鹿, di fronte al tracollo dell'auto elettrica, anzich脙漏 fare retromarcia sul Green Deal in modo del tutto incoerente, decidete di investire 850 miliardi di euro per costruire carri armati. Ma da quando i carri armati sono green?
E lo fate, peraltro, senza alcun mandato parlamentare e chiedendo, ancora una volta, enormi sacrifici a quei cittadini che, a causa delle vostre politiche scellerate, non riescono ad arrivare alla fine del mese.
Il problema 脙篓 che, mentre qui dentro si perde tempo a giocare a Risiko, l脙聽 fuori la Cina ogni giorno ci soffia quote di mercato e ogni minuto perso per salvare le nostre imprese 脙篓 una pietra tombale sulla competitivit脙聽 europea.
(La Presidente toglie la parola all'oratrice)</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T20:59:53</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_328"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_119">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_119</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Maria Guzenina</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_S&amp;D"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_39">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_39</del:identifier>
    <del:text>(Mr脗聽Della Valle unfurled a flag)
Please, please come on. No blue card then.
I might remind you that this is probably against the rules. This is a parliament. It comes from parlare. Yes, I know it's the European flag and we love it.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T10:33:45</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_160">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_160</del:identifier>
    <del:text>We are now continuing with our debate.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:59:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_193">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_193</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Come donna, madre, magistrato e deputata al Parlamento europeo, ritengo di rappresentare emblematicamente la molta strada, non facile, che 脙篓 stata fatta sul fronte della parit脙聽 di genere ma, 脙篓 innegabile, non 脙篓 ancora cos脙卢 per tante, troppe donne e ragazze!
脙聢 infatti ancora lungo il cammino per assicurare l芒聙聶attuazione concreta dell芒聙聶art. 23 della Carta dei diritti fondamentali dell'Unione europea che stabilisce: 芒聙聹La parit脙聽 tra uomini e donne in tutti i campi, compreso in materia di occupazione, di lavoro e di retribuzione.芒聙聺
Bene quindi l芒聙聶introduzione della roadmap dell芒聙聶UE per i diritti delle donne, presentata dalla Commissione nei suoi primi 100 giorni di lavoro, che rappresenta un rinnovato impulso a rafforzare la parit脙聽 di genere, consolidando i progressi compiuti nell'ambito della strategia 2020-2025, e fornisce una panoramica dettagliata degli ambiti in cui sono necessari ulteriori interventi.
C芒聙聶脙篓 ancora molto lavoro da fare: per far fronte alla piaga silenziosa e inaccettabile della violenza contro le donne che, purtroppo, non accenna a fermarsi, per colmare il divario retributivo di genere e, soprattutto, per garantire concretamente, ad ogni donna, la libert脙聽 di non dover mai scegliere tra vita professionale e vita familiare!</del:text>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_140"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_167">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_167</del:identifier>
    <del:text></del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:07:07</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_118"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_360">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_360</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Reinhold Lopatka</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_510">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_510</del:identifier>
    <del:text>En lo que afecta a las comunidades kurdas parece haber esperanza a los dos lados de la frontera, aunque con l脙鲁gicas y ritmos diferentes. El acuerdo inicial alcanzado anoche tiene al menos dos ra脙颅ces: las masacres del ataque de estos d脙颅as y el riesgo de descontrol, y la llamada de 脙聳calan al desarme y disoluci脙鲁n de la organizaci脙鲁n terrorista PKK, cuyas ondas han alcanzado a las fuerzas militantes turcas del norte de Siria.
Es un acuerdo inicial y, por tanto, sujeto a sacudidas, pero nuestra voluntad pol脙颅tica hacia ese marco es que haya una Siria unida, soberana, inclusiva y en manos de los propios sirios. Por lo tanto, fuera Turqu脙颅a, fuera Israel y fuera Rusia.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:14:14</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_361"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_33">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_33</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Milan Uhr脙颅k</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_ESN"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_543">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_543</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Y mientras tanto, 脗驴qu脙漏 est脙隆 haciendo Europa, se脙卤ora comisaria? 脗驴Mirar hacia otro lado para contentar a Trump? 脗驴El mismo Trump que acaba de detener a un estudiante palestino en la Universidad de Columbia para impedir que pueda expresarse libremente y seguir intentando que no se cumplan los derechos humanos ni en Gaza ni en los Estados Unidos?
Se脙卤or脙颅as, los valores europeos no son solo un eslogan, se tienen que cumplir cada d脙颅a y, para ello, debemos proteger los derechos humanos en Gaza, aumentar la ayuda humanitaria, hacer misiones de paz y construir, de verdad, la paz en todo el mundo.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T23:05:26</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_377"/>
  </rdf:Description>
