    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_180</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Vreau s脛聝 v脛聝 mai spun ceva: 脙庐n 脠聸ara mea, 脙庐n 8 martie s脛聝rb脛聝torim 芒聙聯 脠聶i 脙庐n toat脛聝 lumea, bine脙庐n脠聸eles 芒聙聯 Ziua Interna脠聸ional脛聝 a Femeii, dar 脙庐n 9 martie e Ziua B脛聝rbatului 脠聶i ne respect脛聝m reciproc 脠聶i eu cred 脙庐n acest parteneriat pentru a putea s脛聝 facem proiecte 脙庐mpreun脛聝. Conduc o asocia脠聸ie a femeilor din Rom脙垄nia de 28 de ani 脠聶i crede脠聸i-m脛聝 c脛聝 lucr脛聝m foarte bine cu partenerii b脛聝rba脠聸i. 脙聨n foaia de parcurs, doamn脛聝 comisar脛聝, 脠聶i sunt m脙垄ndr脛聝 c脛聝 sunte脠聸i aici, trebuie s脛聝 vorbi脠聸i 脠聶i cu ceilal脠聸i comisari, s脛聝 avem m脛聝suri concrete. A脠聶a cum am spus 脠聶i la alte dezbateri, nu e suficient s脛聝 dezbatem, ci trebuie s脛聝 avem m脛聝suri concrete pentru a face progrese.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:26:06</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_76"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_104">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_104</del:identifier>
    <del:text>I now pass the floor to Belarusian opposition activist and former political prisoner Palina Sharenda-Panasiuk.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T12:26:21</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_112">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_112</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Yesterday evening, on Russian TV, Vladimir Solovyov, the main propagandist of Putin's regime, attacked, insulted, threatened one of us: Pina Picierno, Vice-President of this House, has been assaulted with terrific violence on Russian TV.
And then you had campaigns of trolls and bots inside our own territory. So today it's time for us to show solidarity in front of fascist propagandists ...
(The President cut off the speaker)</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T12:54:32</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_68"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_487">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_487</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Clean Industrial Deal je prezentovan脙陆 ako ve脛戮kolep脙陆 pl脙隆n na z脙隆chranu plan脙漏ty a posilnenie eur脙鲁pskeho priemyslu. No v skuto脛聧nosti? Je to 脛聫al脜隆脙颅 drah脙陆 v脙陆strel do tmy od bruselskej elity, ktor脙隆 ignoruje realitu na脜隆ich n脙隆rodov.

Tento deal s脛戮ubuje zelen脙潞 bud脙潞cnos脜楼, ale za ak脙潞 cenu? Pr脙颅sne regul脙隆cie a miliardov脙漏 dot脙隆cie do vetra 芒聙聯 doslova 芒聙聯 zvy脜隆uj脙潞 n脙隆klady pre na脜隆e firmy, ktor脙漏 u脜戮 teraz bojuj脙潞 s konkurenciou z 脛聦脙颅ny a Ameriky. Tam si emisie nerie脜隆ia, vyr脙隆baj脙潞 lacno a efekt脙颅vne, k脙陆m my tu top脙颅me peniaze da脜聢ov脙陆ch poplatn脙颅kov v byrokracii, sol脙隆rnych paneloch a vrtuliach. V脙陆sledok? Strat脙颅me pracovn脙漏 miesta, presunieme v脙陆robu mimo E脙職 a glob脙隆lne emisie sa nezmenia 芒聙聯 len sa pres脜楼ahuj脙潞 inde.

P脙陆tam sa v脙隆s: Ko脛戮ko e脜隆te zaplat脙颅me za zelen脙漏 il脙潞zie? Ko脛戮ko fabr脙颅k sa mus脙颅 zatvori脜楼, ko脛戮ko 脛戮ud脙颅 pr脙颅s脜楼 o pr脙隆cu, k脙陆m si prizn脙隆me, 脜戮e tento deal nie je rie脜隆en脙颅m, ale probl脙漏mom? My nepotrebujeme 脛聫al脜隆ie ideologick脙漏 experimenty 芒聙聯 my potrebujeme pragmatizmus, konkurencieschopnos脜楼 a slobodu rozhodova脜楼 o vlastnej bud脙潞cnosti.

脛聨akujem</del:text>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_67"/>
  </rdf:Description>
