  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_153">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_153</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Nevertheless, to my question: you don't see yourself as a threat to women's rights? Because I am so much more afraid of you and what you can do with your power here 芒聙聯 to my rights, to my girls' rights 芒聙聯 with your anti-gender approach and with your racist approach. Don't you consider yourself as a threat to us?</del:text>
