  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_82">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_82</del:identifier>
    <del:text>What I'm talking about are the projects that will substantially increase our ability to defend, and make it much more effective, and save money 芒聙聯 for example, anti-missile defence, drone defence, electronic defence, and so on.
It would be 芒聙聯 and I guess you understand 芒聙聯 much more effective to make it together than try to develop 10 or 20 different systems at the same time. We don't each need to reinvent the wheel.</del:text>
