  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_188">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_188</del:identifier>
    <del:text>87脗聽000 women across the world will die because they're women. Over the course of a decade, that's the city of Amsterdam. 96脗聽% of AI芒聙聭generated content known as deepfakes are pornographic in nature, sexualised content targeting women and young girls. We know this from reports that 99脗聽% of them are indeed women and young girls.
The foundation of gender equality is built on the rights to live free from all injustices. Yet, at the current pace of progress, gender equality will only be achieved by 2158. Yet I ask, what are we doing in here for the 229 million citizens that elected us and expect us to do better?</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:36:42</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_138"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_370">
