  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_201">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_201</del:identifier>
    <del:text>脙聙 cette fin, nous devons avoir un cadre rigoureux, clarifier les d脙漏finitions des m脙漏dicaments critiques et des p脙漏nuries, assurer la transparence de la cha脙庐ne de valeur, avoir des conditionnalit脙漏s sur les march脙漏s publics et favoriser des march脙漏s ou des achats collectifs 脙聽 l芒聙聶脙漏chelle europ脙漏enne 芒聙聯脗聽autrement dit, la solidarit脙漏 europ脙漏enne. Ce qui est le plus important, pour les socialistes, c芒聙聶est peut-脙陋tre de garantir 脙聽 toutes et 脙聽 tous en Europe l芒聙聶acc脙篓s aux m脙漏dicaments 芒聙聯脗聽leur disponibilit脙漏 un prix accessible, et des stocks disponibles脗聽芒聙聯, et ce partout, au plus pr脙篓s des gens. Il s芒聙聶agit bien, 脙聽 travers ce texte, d芒聙聶une politique de sant脙漏 publique autant que d芒聙聶une politique industrielle.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:54:19</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_146"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_509">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_509</del:identifier>
    <del:text>It is vital for the country to continue developing national unity. It's good to see that the government finalised an agreement with the Kurdish-led Syrian Democratic Forces, and they have to use the chance to integrate them into the national army and into the governing structure.
While these developments are promising, challenges, of course, persist. The recent violence in Latakia, where more than 1脗聽500 people lost their lives, highlights the fragile security situation. And this needs our engagement. No Syrian should live in fear anymore. Therefore, it is positive that we discuss Syria and that we work for a good future for the Syrian people. They deserve it.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:12:58</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_360"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_212">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_212</del:identifier>
    <del:text>COVID pandemija labai ai脜隆kiai pademonstravo, k脛聟 rei脜隆kia b脜芦ti priklausomiems nuo tre脛聧i脜鲁j脜鲁 脜隆ali脜鲁 gaminamos produkcijos, ta脛聧iau tuo pa脛聧iu metu parod脛聴, kad esant pakankamai valiai Europos S脛聟junga gali per trump脛聟 laik脛聟 mobilizuoti l脛聴脜隆as svarbi脜鲁 preparat脜鲁 k脜芦rimui ir gamybai.
Globalia ekonomika gr脛炉stas tik脛聴jimas, kad neb脜芦tina visko gamintis patiems, nul脛聴m脛聴 svarbi脜鲁 veikli脜鲁j脜鲁 med脜戮iag脜鲁 gamybos i脜隆k脛聴lim脛聟 脛炉 tre脛聧i脛聟sias 脜隆alis ir su tuo susijusius vaist脜鲁 tr脜芦kumus. Apie 脜隆i脜鲁 problem脜鲁 sprendim脛聟 jau galvojama, ta脛聧iau a脜隆 pasigendu suvokimo, kad egzistuoja ir santykinis ypatingos svarbos vaist脜鲁 tr脜芦kumas, kuris yra susij脛聶s ne su fiziniu vaist脜鲁 tr脜芦kumu, o su santykiniu tr脜芦kumu, kuomet vaistas yra tiesiog ne脛炉perkamas. Tod脛聴l a脜隆 noriu papra脜隆yti svarstant ypatingos svarbos vaist脜鲁 fail脛聟 nepamir脜隆ti inovatyvi脜鲁 vaist脜鲁 ir numatyti galimyb脛聶 sukurti pagalbos 脜隆alims mechanizm脛聟, realizuojam脛聟 per savanori脜隆k脛聟 bendr脜鲁 vaist脜鲁 deryb脜鲁 ir pirkimo mechanizm脛聟.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:09:18</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_156"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_220">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_220</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Jedn脙陆m zo sp脙麓sobov, ako tieto nerovnosti vyrovna脜楼, je spolo脛聧n脙陆 eur脙鲁psky pr脙颅stup k r脙陆chlej脜隆ej dostupnosti liekov. Pand脙漏mia COVID-19 n脙隆m uk脙隆zala, ako r脙陆chlo a ne脛聧akane m脙麓脜戮eme 脛聧eli脜楼 kritick脙漏mu nedostatku liekov, a nem脙麓脜戮eme si dovoli脜楼 by脜楼 z脙隆visl脙颅 od dod脙隆vok z tret脙颅ch kraj脙颅n, ako je 脛聦脙颅na 脛聧i India. Mus脙颅me investova脜楼 do eur脙鲁pskych kapac脙颅t na v脙陆robu liekov, podpori脜楼 v脙陆skum a zabezpe脛聧i脜楼 dostupnos脜楼 liekov pre v脜隆etk脙陆ch. To v脜隆ak zvl脙隆dneme len spolo脛聧ne. Obrana, 脙隆no, konkurencieschopnos脜楼, 脙隆no, no rovnak脙漏 脙隆no plat脙颅 pre kvalitn脙潞 zdravotn脙潞 starostlivos脜楼 pre v脜隆etk脙陆ch ob脛聧anov a ob脛聧ianky Eur脙鲁py.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:20:50</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_163"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_279">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_279</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Kl脙隆ra Dobrev</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_S&amp;D"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_233">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_233</del:identifier>
    <del:name>David McAllister</del:name>
