  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_318">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_318</del:identifier>
    <del:text>I will ask my colleagues to remember that you have the blue-card option very soon, so you have a chance to ask questions for your colleagues. And when you don't have the blue card, please let people speak quietly. Please, colleagues. Thank you.
So now we are here where I open up for the blue-card option. We always do that after the first round of speakers on behalf of the political groups. And we ended that.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T17:58:00</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_1"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_537">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_537</del:identifier>
    <del:text>The fact is that after Israel once again cut off electricity to Gaza, nine out of ten people no longer have access to safe drinking water. Nine out of ten.
The fact is that after Israel once again halted the delivery of humanitarian aid to Gaza, the genocide is only escalating. Generations are being wiped out before our eyes. And still the powerful are turning a blind one or worse.
If those of you who had even a shred 芒聙聯 just a shred 芒聙聯 of humanity in you, you would not look away. You would not excuse the inexcusable. You would do something that should have been done long ago. You would deliver.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:57:42</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_374"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_511">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_511</del:identifier>
    <del:text>脙聹dv脙露zlend脜聭 a kurd vezet脜聭kkel val脙鲁 megegyez脙漏s, az is, ami n脙漏lk脙录l nincs egys脙漏ges Sz脙颅ria. Elej脙漏t kell venni a k脙录l脙露nb脙露z脜聭 vall脙隆si, etnikai csoportok megk脙录l脙露nb脙露ztet脙漏s脙漏nek. Nem csak a kisebbs脙漏gi jogokr脙鲁l van sz脙鲁, ahogyan ezt a helyi kereszt脙漏ny egyh脙隆zi vezet脜聭k megfogalmazt脙隆k. Sz脙颅ria minden k脙露z脙露ss脙漏g脙漏nek egyenl脜聭 szabads脙隆gjogokat kell 脙漏lveznie, ide脙漏rtve a vall脙隆sszabads脙隆got is. Ebben kell Eur脙鲁p脙隆nak tart脙鲁s strat脙漏giai t脙隆mogat脙隆st ny脙潞jtania. A j脙露v脜聭 heti sz脙颅riai konferencia lehet脜聭s脙漏get ad az EU-tag脙隆llamok sz脙隆m脙隆ra, hogy biztos脙颅ts脙隆k az Uni脙鲁 hiteles humanit脙隆rius szerepv脙隆llal脙隆s脙隆t, 脙漏s tegyenek az 脙潞jj脙隆脙漏p脙颅t脙漏s脙漏rt. Vagyis lehet脜聭v脙漏 tegy脙漏k a 14 milli脙鲁 elv脙隆ndorolt sz脙颅riai hazat脙漏r脙漏s脙漏t 脙漏s t脙漏nyleg az orsz脙隆g egyben tart脙隆s脙隆t. L脙隆tni kell, sz脙隆mukra munkahely, eg脙漏szs脙漏g脙录gyi ell脙隆t脙隆s, gyermekeiknek oktat脙隆s kell. Ma 3,7 milli脙鲁 gyermek egyszer脜卤en Sz脙颅ri脙隆ban nem j脙隆r iskol脙隆ba. Ezek a t脙漏nyek.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:15:28</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_362"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_166">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_166</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Te v脙陇ititte juuri 脙陇sken, ett脙陇 t脙陇脙陇ll脙陇 puhutaan puppua ja alistetaan miehi脙陇. Mill脙陇 tavalla naisten oikeuksien esiin tuominen alistaa miehi脙陇? Ei mill脙陇脙陇n tavalla. Vastatkaa, mihin perustatte v脙陇itteenne?</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:06:04</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_119"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_223">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_223</del:identifier>
    <del:text>A betegek helyzet脙漏nek jav脙颅t脙隆sa 脙漏rdek脙漏ben kiemelten fontos a gy脙鲁gyszerek el脙漏rhet脜聭s脙漏ge 脙漏s megfizethet脜聭s脙漏ge, mik脙露zben biztos脙颅tjuk az eur脙鲁pai gy脙鲁gyszeripar versenyk脙漏pess脙漏g脙漏t 脙漏s rezilienci脙隆j脙隆t. Fontos hangs脙潞lyozni, hogy a Critical Medicines Act ne n脙露velje az adminisztrat脙颅v terheket, 脙漏s ne legyen jogi 脙隆tfed脙漏s, p脙漏ld脙隆ul a gy脙鲁gyszercsomaghi脙隆nnyal foglalkoz脙鲁 r脙漏sz脙漏vel. 脙聹dv脙露zl脙露m a bemutatott javaslatot, 脙漏s k脙露sz脙露n脙露m V脙隆rhelyi biztos 脙潞rnak 脙漏s csapat脙隆nak, hogy ilyen gyorsan elk脙漏sz脙颅tett脙漏k azt.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:25:00</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_166"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_460">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
