  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_246">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_246</del:identifier>
    <del:text>We need Member States to take responsibility and clean up their act, but the proposed return regulation lets them off the hook. It blames and punishes returnees and countries of origin. It gives Member States a blank cheque to dump people in legal and humanitarian limbo in third countries without any prospect of a durable solution. So more suffering, migratory movements back to Europe, and millions 芒聙聯 if not billions 芒聙聯 in wasted taxpayers' money.
We had the chance to finally get it right and make returns work by fixing the gaps, forcing the rules and focusing on durable solutions. But this is just a shameless appeasement of the far right. A Trojan horse that, under the false guise of toughness, will only lead us further astray.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T16:07:44</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_181"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_213">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_213</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Depuis trop longtemps, nous avons laiss脙漏 nos m脙漏dicaments critiques devenir les otages des d脙漏localisations et des tensions g脙漏opolitiques. D脙漏pendre de quelques usines 脙聽 l芒聙聶autre bout du monde, c芒聙聶est accepter l芒聙聶impuissance face 脙聽 l芒聙聶urgence. L芒聙聶acte l脙漏gislatif sur les m脙漏dicaments critiques doit donc b脙垄tir une v脙漏ritable souverainet脙漏 pharmaceutique europ脙漏enne. Cela passera par une l脙漏gislation ambitieuse: relocalisation strat脙漏gique des productions, 脙漏tablissement de stocks de s脙漏curit脙漏 et coordination renforc脙漏e entre les 脙聣tats membres.
Il ne s芒聙聶agit pas seulement d芒聙聶un enjeu industriel; il s芒聙聶agit 脙漏galement d芒聙聶un imp脙漏ratif de sant脙漏 publique.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:10:36</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_157"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_179">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_179</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Istra脜戮ivanje objavljeno u studenom pro脜隆le godine pokazuje kako je nasilje nad 脜戮enama i dalje gotovo obi脛聧ajno, 脛聧ak i u Europi. Svaka tre脛聡a 脜戮ena do脜戮ivjela je fizi脛聧ko ili seksualno nasilje u odrasloj dobi, a svaka peta se suo脛聧ila s obiteljskim nasiljem.
I dok stariji oblici nasilja nad 脜戮enama nisu iskorijenjeni, na脜戮alost svjedo脛聧imo novima. Posljednje godi脜隆nje izvje脜隆脛聡e o ravnopravnosti spolova ukazuje kako je nasilje nad 脜戮enama na internetu postalo sveprisutno. Od 2023. godine 97 posto online prijava seksualnog zlostavljanja djece na internetu odnosilo se na seksualno zlostavljanje djevojaka i djevoj脛聧ica.
Europska unija ima najnaprednije zakonodavstvo koje obuhva脛聡a za脜隆titu od nasilja na internetu, uklju脛聧uju脛聡i nasilje koje se temelji na neeti脛聧kom kori脜隆tenju umjetne inteligencije, ali samo zakonodavstvo nije dovoljno. Moramo educirati 脜戮ene, a osobito djevoj脛聧ice kako bismo se osna脜戮ili u pogledu nasilja svih vrsta, uklju脛聧uju脛聡i nasilje na internetu i nasilje putem dru脜隆tvenih mre脜戮a.
Kao zastupnici u parlamentu moramo u脛聧initi sve 脜隆to je u na脜隆oj mo脛聡i kako bi se 脜戮ene osje脛聡ale sigurno i slobodno.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:24:47</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_131"/>
  </rdf:Description>
