  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_169">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_169</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Thanks to this roadmap, we now have a path forward, and I am honoured to shadow its implementing strategy, but what should we do? First, we need to combat violence, including integrating consent-based rape laws. Second, we must ensure equality in all areas of life and work, and this means gender mainstreaming and gender budgeting. It is not an ideology.
Commissioner Lahbib is not here with us, but I want Commissioner M脙庐nzatu to tell her that we really rely on her, because promoting equality is the key to a future where women 芒聙聯 but eventually all of us 芒聙聯 can live free from fear and discrimination. And the EU needs to lead this gender equality fight that we have worldwide, especially in those insecure times when geo-policy is changing.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T14:09:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_121"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_299">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_299</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Maar het moet me toch van het hart: de onzin, de leugens, de stigmatisering van extreemrechts hier in dit halfrond tarten alle verbeelding. Ik ga vragen aan die zijde. 脙聣脙漏n: kijk eens in de spiegel. Als jullie geboren worden in een land in oorlog en chemisch gebombardeerd worden, ga je niet vluchten? En twee: u mag van geluk spreken dat u geboren bent in Europa, in een land in vrede.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T17:21:41</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_78"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_248">
