  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_349">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_349</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Nem脙隆me desiatky rokov, mo脜戮no m脙隆me mesiace, aby sme vytvorili spolo脛聧n脙潞 obranu, ktor脙隆 Rusko odstra脜隆脙颅, ale presne o tom odstra脜隆en脙颅 je t脙隆to debata. O asert脙颅vnosti a o na脜隆ej jednote. A o tom by mala by脜楼 aj debata o bielej knihe. 脙聛no, bude n脙隆s to nie脛聧o st脙隆脜楼, ale bude to cena prevencie a udr脜戮ate脛戮n脙漏ho mieru ur脛聧ite ni脜戮脜隆ia ako cena vojny. A aby zv脙陆脜隆en脙漏 n脙隆klady nepadli na t脙陆ch najbli脜戮脜隆脙颅ch, na to m脙隆me v Eur脙鲁pskej 脙潞nii a v 脛聧lensk脙陆ch 脜隆t脙隆toch n脙隆stroje.
Tak脜戮e v脛聧era bolo neskoro. My sa mus脙颅me poisti脜楼 a invest脙颅cia do spolo脛聧nej bezpe脛聧nosti je na脜隆ou poistkou. Eur脙鲁pa sa mus脙颅 br脙隆ni脜楼.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T18:42:42</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_121"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_309">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_309</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Anja Hazekamp</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_The Left"/>
