  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_411">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_411</del:identifier>
    <del:text>脙聨n acest sens, Rom脙垄nia are un poten脠聸ial semnificativ de a deveni un actor important 脙庐n industria de ap脛聝rare european脛聝, 脙庐ns脛聝 pentru aceasta trebuie s脛聝 ac脠聸ion脛聝m rapid 脠聶i strategic. Este necesar s脛聝 simplific脛聝m procedurile administrative, s脛聝 implic脛聝m mediul de afaceri, s脛聝 cre脛聝m parteneriate strategice cu statele membre 脠聶i s脛聝 dezvolt脛聝m proiecte concrete, care s脛聝 contribuie direct la 脙庐nt脛聝rirea capacit脛聝脠聸ilor de ap脛聝rare. 脙聨n acela脠聶i timp, trebuie s脛聝 elabor脛聝m 脠聶i s脛聝 implement脛聝m un plan na脠聸ional de dezvoltare a industriei de ap脛聝rare, care s脛聝 alinieze Rom脙垄nia la standardele 脠聶i obiectivele europene.

Avem nevoie de o viziune european脛聝 de ap脛聝rare care s脛聝 r脛聝spund脛聝 eficient provoc脛聝rilor externe, dar 脠聶i s脛聝 ofere o perspectiv脛聝 strategic脛聝 pe termen lung. Doar printr-o abordare colectiv脛聝 脠聶i unitar脛聝 putem construi o Europ脛聝 capabil脛聝 s脛聝 fac脛聝 fa脠聸脛聝 amenin脠聸脛聝rilor actuale 脠聶i viitoare.</del:text>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_295"/>
  </rdf:Description>
