  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_275">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_275</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Evin Incir</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_S&amp;D"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_210">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_210</del:identifier>
    <del:text>I agree that in some Member States, medicine is more accessible than in others, and this is something we shouldn't accept. We should work together to have a European Union, a true European health Union, where every European citizen has equal access to medicines.
I'm really sure that we as a Parliament together can work on this commonly shared aim.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T15:07:03</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_153"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_364">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_364</del:identifier>
    <del:text>So Europe has to grow up and be strong 芒聙聯 both economically and militarily 芒聙聯 so that we can take care of our own independently, hopefully with good cooperation with the United States some time after Trump's term. But if not, we still have to be able to do it independently. We have people, we have money, we have innovation. We can do it.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T18:59:33</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_261"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_32">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_32</del:identifier>
    <del:text>We must act swiftly. Our defence industries need a framework that enables them to deliver, both through cooperation and national initiatives. That means cutting bureaucracy, simplifying the processes, providing real financial access and bringing energy prices down. We cannot have both an overambitious green transition and a fully capable military. Resources are finite. Europe must decide what it values most.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T10:24:32</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_28"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_276">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_276</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Mika Aaltola</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_PPE"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_140">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_140</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Dans un monde o脙鹿 1脗聽femme sur 8 dans le monde a d脙漏j脙聽 subi un viol ou une agression sexuelle enfant, le fait que les hommes ne suivent pas de stage en d脙漏construction, financ脙漏 par l芒聙聶argent public, ce m脙陋me argent qui manque pour installer des maternit脙漏s ou des services gyn脙漏cologiques sur tous nos territoires, rel脙篓ve plus de l芒聙聶脙漏lucubration de gauche que du f脙漏minisme sens脙漏. D脙漏fendre les droits des femmes, ce n芒聙聶est pas imposer des dogmes; c芒聙聶est assurer leur s脙漏curit脙漏 et leur dignit脙漏 face aux vraies menaces, et avoir 脙漏galement la lucidit脙漏 de reconna脙庐tre que certaines cultures sont ouvertement misogynes. Quand je dis cela, je ne parle pas 脙漏videmment d芒聙聶un patriarcat europ脙漏en fantasm脙漏.
Alors, ma question, largement partag脙漏e par des millions de femmes qui attendent qu芒聙聶on change leur quotidien, est la suivante: qu芒聙聶est-ce que nous en avons 脙聽 faire de vos propositions fumeuses sur la th脙漏orie du genre, l芒聙聶aide 脙聽 la transition de genre ou l芒聙聶脙漏criture inclusive, quand des millions de femmes craignent de sortir ne serait-ce que dans leur propre rue?
(L'oratrice accepte une question carton bleu)</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T13:35:09</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_103"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_84">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_84</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Mano 脜戮inia viena 芒聙聯 Europa bus stipri, jei pad脛聴sime Ukrainai laim脛聴ti. Ir mes galime, tik reikia patik脛聴ti, kad galime. 芒聙聻ReArm Europe芒聙聹 turi b脜芦ti 脛炉gyvendinama solidariai tarp Europos S脛聟jungos nari脜鲁 ir solidariai su Ukraina, kuri jau yra ES nar脛聴 de facto, nes savo krauju gina mus.
Ukrainos fronte sprend脜戮iamas Europos likimas. Ka脜戮kas paskai脛聧iavo, kad iki 脜隆iol kiekvienam Europos S脛聟jungos pilie脛聧iui Europos karin脛聴 parama Ukrainai nekainavo n脛聴 dviej脜鲁 puodeli脜鲁 kavos. Valstyb脛聴s nar脛聴s tikrai gali skirti Ukrainai daugiau. Sutarkim d脛聴l ne ma脜戮iau kaip 0,25脗聽proc. nuo BVP i脜隆 kiekvienos 脜隆alies. I脜隆kelkim ambicij脛聟: Ukraina 芒聙聯 Europos S脛聟jungos nar脛聴 iki 2030脗聽m. Pasikartokim istorijos pamokas ir priimkim i脜隆脜隆脜芦kius. 芒聙聻Keep calm, carry on芒聙聹 芒聙聯 Winston Churchill.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T11:33:53</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_72"/>
  </rdf:Description>
