  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_520">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_520</del:identifier>
    <del:text>In addition, we need to be vigilant towards the information manipulation by foreign actors to steer further violence and instability. Those foreign actors do not share our vision for a stable and inclusive Syria.
It is for the EU to support the transition and to become a reliable partner for Syria's future. The coming days and months will be decisive.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:30:22</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_2"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_62">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_62</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Protams, Eiropadomes lemtais par 脜隆iem 800 miljardiem eiro ir solis pareiz脛聛 virzien脛聛. Ta脛聧u uzdosim jaut脛聛jumu, vai jau tr脛芦s gadus atpaka脛录 m脛聯s nevar脛聯j脛聛m pacelt 脜隆o klauzulu, kas liedza 650 miljardus dal脛芦bvalst脛芦m ieguld脛芦t milit脛聛raj脛聛 industrij脛聛 un aizsardz脛芦b脛聛. Un ar脛芦 脜隆ie 150 miljardi no SAFE programmas, 脜隆脛路iet, tiks aplikti ar p脛聛rliekiem nosac脛芦jumiem 芒聙聰 脜隆odien dzird脛聯tiem no Eiropas Komisijas priek脜隆s脛聯d脛聯t脛聛jas puses, 芒聙聰 kas var脛聯tu piemekl脛聯t l脛芦dz脛芦gu likteni, k脛聛 mums iet ar Atvese脛录o脜隆anas un notur脛芦bas meh脛聛nismu.
Kas b脜芦tu Eiropai j脛聛dara 脜隆aj脛聛 iz脜隆脛路iro脜隆aj脛聛 br脛芦d脛芦? Manupr脛聛t, p脛聛rliecino脜隆i 脛聛tri so脛录i, piem脛聯ram, palielin脛聛t sankcijas krievu 脛聯nu flotei vismaz l脛芦dz ASV sankciju apm脛聯ram pret tiem, nepirkt Krievijas sa脜隆脛路idrin脛聛to g脛聛zi, konfisc脛聯t iesald脛聯tos Krievijas resursus un nos脜芦t脛芦t Ukrainai pal脛芦dz脛芦bu, nu, vismaz apm脛聯ram 1% no IKP milit脛聛raj脛聛 pus脛聯.
J脛聛, nav pat脛芦kama ASV administr脛聛cijas poz脛芦cija, ta脛聧u Eiropas lab脛聛k脛聛 atbilde b脜芦tu r脛芦c脛芦ba 芒聙聰 demonstr脛聛cija, un tas par脛聛d脛芦tu to, ka vien脛芦g脛聛 iz脜隆脛路iro脜隆脛聛 iesp脛聯ja mums ir saglab脛聛t (NATO ietvaros) stingru Rietumu poz脛芦ciju dro脜隆脛芦bas jom脛聛.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T11:05:57</del:timestamp>
