  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_507">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_507</del:identifier>
    <del:text>The EU needs to invest in the political economy of reconciliation as a matter of urgency. The Syria conference that takes place next Monday is the ninth one, but different from every other 芒聙聯 for some very obvious reasons and some less obvious reasons. The most obvious is the change in regime. The less obvious is the fact that international aid has collapsed in the last 12脗聽months.
My plea to you, Commissioner, is to concentrate on the agricultural industry, to concentrate on replanting, on irrigation, on bakeries, on the core of the regrowth of the Syrian economy and the pathway to that sustainable peace.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:10:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_358"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_77">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_77</del:identifier>
    <del:name>脦聯脦碌脦卢脦麓脦路脧聜 脦聯脦碌脦卢脦麓脦路</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_ECR"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_377">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_377</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Temos de garantir que a Uni脙拢o est脙隆 preparada para enfrentar todo o tipo de amea脙搂as, desde as h脙颅bridas 脙聽s convencionais, estabelecendo uma forte dissuas脙拢o, reduzindo as nossas depend脙陋ncias e refor脙搂ando a nossa autonomia.
Mas qualquer ideia de tentar escolher entre investimentos em seguran脙搂a e defesa, ou em coes脙拢o social, ou em coes脙拢o, resultaria numa derrota certa em ambas as frentes. Qualquer estrat脙漏gia de investimento tem de ser abrangente, ter脙隆 de abordar tanto as nossas vulnerabilidades em capacidades militares como as do nosso tecido social.
Estas s脙拢o decis脙碌es estrat脙漏gicas para a Uni脙拢o e para o seu futuro. Isso significa que o Parlamento Europeu n脙拢o deve ser exclu脙颅do dos processos de decis脙拢o no que diz respeito aos programas de despesa subjacentes 脙聽s op脙搂脙碌es tomadas para a Uni脙拢o Europeia.
A recente proposta do ReArm inclui novos empr脙漏stimos conjuntos com base no artigo 122.脗潞 do Tratado sobre o Funcionamento da Uni脙拢o Europeia 芒聙聰 e n脙拢o podemos deixar de lamentar o recurso, novamente, a este artigo, que exclui o Parlamento da decis脙拢o.脗聽O Parlamento Europeu 脙漏 a 脙潞nica institui脙搂脙拢o com poderes legislativos, or脙搂amentais e de supervis脙拢o, com legitimidade democr脙隆tica conferida pela elei脙搂脙拢o direta dos seus membros.
Estamos c脙隆 para decidir em prol dos cidad脙拢os europeus.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T19:17:27</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_271"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_50">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_50</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Therefore, it is essential that the EU strengthens its support for Ukraine. In addition, the EU should set a strategic goal of reducing our dependencies on the US. This means: creating a European security architecture, redirecting all financing currently going to the US arms industry to Europe; reducing energy dependencies; and limiting the powers of the digital oligarchs.
Changes to the fiscal rules must enable all of these investments. I do understand that the goal might also require more investment in European defence. But it would be a historic mistake to finance this by cutting welfare, because that would only cement the rise to power of Putin's and Trump's allies in Europe: the extreme right. And for once, the EU needs to be smarter than this.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T10:48:20</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_42"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/creitem3">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Topic"/>
    <del:identifier>creitem3</del:identifier>
    <del:name>European Council meetings and European security (joint debate)</del:name>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_130">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Participant"/>
    <del:identifier>participant_130</del:identifier>
    <del:name>Marc Angel</del:name>
    <del:isAffiliatedWith rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/org_S&amp;D"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_449">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_449</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Dans le m脙陋me esprit, ce pacte doit aussi faire de l芒聙聶Europe la cheffe de file de l芒聙聶脙漏conomie circulaire 芒聙聯脗聽entre autres脗聽芒聙聯 dans le monde, afin de diminuer notre d脙漏pendance aux mati脙篓res premi脙篓res critiques. C芒聙聶est pour cela que nous saluons le fait que vous ayez repris dans ce pacte le principe consistant 脙聽 n芒聙聶acheter qu芒聙聶une seule fois: une fois les mat脙漏riaux entr脙漏s sur notre territoire, nous devons les garder ici et ils doivent y rester. En les recyclant et en les r脙漏utilisant, nous r脙漏duisons notre d脙漏pendance, nous baissons les co脙禄ts et nous s脙漏curisons nos ressources.
Gr脙垄ce 脙聽 une 脙漏nergie propre et 脙聽 une 脙漏conomie circulaire, nous b脙垄tirons une Europe plus forte et plus autonome.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T20:46:39</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_320"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_502">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_502</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Und so geht es weiter. F脙录r kommenden Montag l脙陇dt Frau von der Leyen zu einer Geberkonferenz nach Br脙录ssel脗聽芒聙聯 auch Vertreter aus Damaskus sind eingeladen. Ich habe ja schon einige verr脙录ckte Dinge hier im Haus gesehen, aber das sprengt wirklich alle Dimensionen. Trotz Massaker an Alewiten und Christen l脙陇dt Frau von der Leyen zur gro脙聼en Spendengala f脙录r den Dschihad in Syrien. Nie wieder sollten Sie hier von einer westlichen Wertegemeinschaft sprechen!
Die Amerikaner werden an der Br脙录sseler Spendengala nicht teilnehmen脗聽芒聙聯 zu Recht. Islamisten bleiben Islamisten, auch wenn sie sich den Bart stutzen und eine Krawatte umbinden.</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T22:03:51</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_354"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_290">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_290</del:identifier>
    <del:text>Sama jsem patn脙隆ct let pracovala p脜聶i navracen脙颅 uprchl脙颅k脜炉 do zem脙颅 p脜炉vodu a v脙颅m, 脜戮e mus脙颅me b脙陆t v na脜隆脙颅 legislativ脛聸 nekompromisn脙颅 a tvrd脙颅. Nov脙隆 p脜聶脙颅sn脛聸j脜隆脙颅 politika n脙隆vrat脜炉 byla nutn脙隆 u脜戮 l脙漏ta. Z脙隆kon o n脙隆vratu mus脙颅 vyslat jasn脙陆 vzkaz: Nep脜聶ich脙隆zejte do Evropy neleg脙隆ln脛聸, proto脜戮e budete vr脙隆ceni zp脛聸t. V nov脙漏m n脙隆vrhu o n脙隆vratech chyb脙颅 povinn脙陆 tlak na t脜聶et脙颅 zem脛聸. Evropsk脙隆 unie mus脙颅 vyu脜戮脙颅t sv脜炉j vliv, aby donutila zem脛聸 p脜聶ij脙颅mat zp脛聸t sv脙漏 ob脛聧any, obchodn脙颅 sankce, v脙颅za nebo konec finan脛聧n脙颅 pomoci. P脜聶ijm脛聸te zp脛聸t sv脙漏 ob脛聧any, jinak...
(P脜聶edsedaj脙颅c脙颅 脜聶e脛聧nici odebrala slovo.)</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-11T17:09:39</del:timestamp>
    <del:madeBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/participant_213"/>
  </rdf:Description>
