  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://w3id.org/deliberation/resource/contribution_137">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/deliberation/ontology#Contribution"/>
    <del:identifier>contribution_137</del:identifier>
    <del:text>My question to you is: would you agree with me that access to contraception and sexual and reproductive rights 芒聙聯 including abortion and abortion pills 芒聙聯 for women in rural areas is something that we should all work on?</del:text>
